Job Portal Backend (Express + MongoDB)

This is the backend for a job portal application built using Node.js, Express, and MongoDB.
It provides APIs for managing users, companies, jobs, and applications, with authentication and cookie handling.

ğŸš€ Features

User authentication & management

Company management

Job postings & listings

Application management

MongoDB connection with Mongoose

CORS enabled for frontend integration

Serves frontend (React/Vite build) from frontend/dist

